snippet.title: Gözlerimde Sonbahar - Kalbe Dokunan Şarkılar
snippet.description:
GÖZLERİMDE SONBAHAR
Bir yolun sonunda kaldım,
Giden sen, kalan bu kalbim.
Yağmurlar vurur yüzüme,
Sanki sen ağlıyorsun içimden.
Bir nefesin izindeyim,
Bir yarım sözün derdindeyim,
Söylesem duyar mısın,
Yalnızlığın dilindeyim.

Gözlerimde sonbahar,
Kalbimde bin hatıra,
Rüzgâr bile sensiz ağlar,
Dön artık, yandım sana.
Gözlerimde sonbahar,
Kalbimde bin hatıra,
Rüzgâr bile sensiz ağlar,
Dön artık, yandım sana.

Bir sözün kaldı kulakta,
Bir fotoğraf soldu duvarda,
Sensiz geçen her akşamda,
Bir yanım eksik hayatta.
İçimde kırık bir dua,
Adın geçer her sabaha,
Ne olur dön bir kez daha,
Kapanmaz bu eski yara .

Gözlerimde sonbahar,
Kalbimde bin hatıra,
Rüzgâr bile sensiz ağlar,
Dön artık, yandım sana.
Gözlerimde sonbahar,
Kalbimde bin hatıra,
Rüzgâr bile sensiz ağlar,
Dön artık, yandım sana.

Dank eines nervtötenden Insekts in Man vs Bee endete ein Job in einem Hightech-Anwesen für Trevor Bingley (Rowan Atkinson) im Chaos. Nun hat er der stressigen Homesitter-Welt den Rücken gekehrt und geht es als Hausmeister an einer Schule etwas ruhiger an. Aber der Frieden ist nur von kurzer Dauer, denn schon lockt das unwiderstehliche Angebot, über Weihnachten auf ein Londoner Luxuspenthouse aufzupassen. Doch als am letzten Schultag niemand den kleinen Jesus aus dem Krippenspiel mit nach Hause nimmt, bekommt Trevor abermals kleine, und sehr unerwartete Gesellschaft. Nun muss er nach dem Penthouse sehen und dabei das Baby zum Bäuerchen animieren. Gelingt es Trevor, wie erhofft, ein friedliches Weihnachtsfest zu feiern, oder enden die Festivitäten im Chaos?

snippet.description:
— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— Grand Theft Auto VI

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Grand Theft Auto VI, the story centers on Lucia, a young criminal struggling to claw her way out of poverty until a buried truth shatters her life and reveals she is the daughter of former Vice City kingpin Tommy Vercetti, now emerging from decades in the shadows. With Jason at her side and the corrupt forces of Leonida closing in, her journey turns from survival to reclamation as blood ties pull her into a legacy built on power, betrayal, and unfinished rule. The trailer suggests that Lucia’s fight is not just against the law but against the fate of inheriting an empire forged in fire, while Tommy’s return reframes the conflict into something far larger than escape — it becomes a battle for succession in the criminal heart of Vice City.

snippet.title: State of Play Japan | November 11, 2025 [English Subtitles]
snippet.description:
This Tuesday, we’re bringing you a special episode of State of Play running for more than 40 minutes, focusing on games created in Japan and across Asia, alongside a few other exciting updates.

From beloved series to distinctive indie creations, the show, hosted by voice actor Yuki Kaji, will be packed with great games, interviews, and new looks at anticipated titles.

State of Play Japan airs on YouTube on November 11 at 2pm PT /  5pm ET /  11pm CEST | November 12 at 7am JST.

The Japanese PlayStation YouTube channel will feature a full Japanese-language version, while the PlayStation YouTube channel will feature the Japanese audio with English subtitles. See you then!

Regarding co-streaming and video-on-demand (VOD)

Please note that this broadcast may include copyrighted content (e.g. licensed music) that PlayStation does not control. We welcome and celebrate our amazing co-streamers and creators, but licensing agreements outside our control could interfere with co-streams or VOD archives of this broadcast. If you’re planning to save this broadcast as a VOD to create recap videos, or to repost clips or segments from the show, we advise omitting any copyrighted music.

#ps5 #ps5games

snippet.title: GTA 6 ist KOMPLETT FERTIG! Trailer 3 HOCHGELADEN? Rockstar Games: Verschiebung Statement - OFFIZIELL
snippet.description:
OMG! GTA 6 ist offiziell verschoben – neuer Termin: 19. November 2026. Begründung: Feinschliff und Qualitätsanspruch. Insider Tom Henderson sagt, das Spiel sei seit Monaten fertig; die zusätzliche Zeit diene nur dem letzten Polishing und diese Verschiebung solle die letzte bleiben. Als nächstes ist sehr wahrscheinlich der nächste große Marketing-Schritt dran: Trailer 3, neue Screenshots und eventuell direkt der Start der Vorbestellung – ähnlich wie beim zweiten Trailer nach kurzer Funkstille. Das Gerücht, der dritte Trailer sei bereits „privat“ auf YouTube hochgeladen, hat aktuell keinen belastbaren Beleg und kann ignoriert werden. Realistisch verläuft die Roadmap so: Trailer 3 (möglicherweise mit Preorder), dann weitere Previews und erste Hands-ons, anschließend der erste offizielle Gameplay-Trailer mit Infos zu Versionen und Anforderungen, später Übergangsthemen für GTA Online und zum Schluss Launch-Trailer, Preload und Day-1-Details. Die Sorge, eine Logo-Umstellung bedeute ein wackelndes Datum, ist unbegründet – maßgeblich ist jetzt der 19.11.2026. Meldungen über interne Entlassungen ändern am Marketing-Takt nichts Wesentliches. Unterm Strich: Der Countdown läuft weiter, der nächste verlässliche Fixpunkt ist Trailer 3 und alles, was nicht offiziell von Rockstar kommt, bleibt Hype-Rauschen.

Hey und willkommen! 
In meinen Videos tauchen wir tief in die Welt von GTA 6 ein und beleuchten alle aktuellen Leaks, Spekulationen und offiziellen Informationen rund um das heiß ersehnte Spiel! Wir analysieren detailliert die neuesten Gerüchte, diskutieren mögliche Schauplätze, Charaktere und Gameplay-Features und schauen uns an, welche offiziellen Fakten Rockstar Games bereits bestätigt hat. Außerdem werfen wir einen Blick auf Insider-Informationen und geben unsere Einschätzungen dazu ab, was uns in Grand Theft Auto VI erwarten könnte. snippet.title: Man Vs Baby | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
After a job looking after a high-tech mansion ended in disaster thanks to an irritating insect in Man vs Bee, Trevor Bingley (Rowan Atkinson) has left the stressful world of housesitting for the quieter life of a school caretaker. That is, until a lucrative offer to look after a luxury London penthouse over Christmas proves too tempting to resist. But on the last day of term, when no one comes to collect the Baby Jesus from the school nativity, Trevor finds himself with another undersized and very unexpected companion. snippet.title: ANNISOKAY - Splinters (OFFICIAL VIDEO)
snippet.description:
#Annisokay #Splinters #AbyssTheFinalChapter #ArisingEmpire
ANNISOKAY's new single 'Splinters ', taken from Abyss - The Final Chapter, out on Nov21.
Pre-order here: https://arisingempire.com/annisokay

SUBSCRIBE to our channel and hit the notification 🔔 to not miss new music: 
https://arisingempire.lnk.to/YTsub

FOLLOW ARISING EMPIRE and keep yourself up to date about your favourite music:
Spotify Official Playlists - https://arisingempire.lnk.to/spotify
Newsletter - https://arisingempire.lnk.to/newsletter
Instagram - https://arisingempire.lnk.to/instagram
TikTok - https://tiktok.com/@arisingempire
Facebook - https://arisingempire.lnk.to/facebook
Twitter - https://arisingempire.lnk.to/twitter
Website - http://www.arising-empire.com

FOLLOW ANNISOKAY:
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/annisokay
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/annisokay
TikTok - https://www.tiktok.com/@annisokayofficial
Twitter - https://twitter.com/annisokay
Website - http://www.annisokay.com

See Annisokay live on tour: https://fanlink.tv/annisokay

Credits:
Produced, mixed and mastered by Christoph Wieczorek at Sawdust Recordings @sawdustrec
Drum and guitars recorded by Vince Ebicht
DoP Peter Leukhardt
Editing, VFX, Color Grading by Christoph Wieczorek

Lyrics: 
I saw you in the rear-view mirror,
Streetlights sketching you in gold.
Just a nod, then you were gone,
Didn't know you’d come undone.

Moments trapped in window glass
Your laugh still dancing in the air
If I’d known that it would end
I would've stayed, I would've cared

One more chance is all I need
To hold you close, never letting you leave
Now I'm living in the past
Holding splinters made of glass
One more chance is all I need
To hold you close, not letting you leave
Now I'm living in the past
Holding splinters made of glass

The promises I never spoke
Will always echo through my chest
I didn’t see you fade like smoke
With only silence for a guest

Little traces still remain
Like your cup still by the sink
Another crack across the pane
And for one moment I cannot think

One more chance is all I need
To hold you close, never letting you leave
Now I'm living in the past
Holding splinters made of glass
One more chance is all I need
To hold you close, not letting you leave
Now I'm living in the past
Holding splinters made of glass
